Use the Complaints Intelligence dashboard to quickly monitor and manage complaints, reduce complaint volume, identify areas for improvement, and make data-driven decisions to enhance complaint management processes.

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled

You can filter the data on the dashboard based on products and services types, complaints type, complaints sub-type, status, financial accounts, duration and compare the data with a previous period to analyze progress.
